# Feature Images for MioChat (Product 3)

Place the following images in this directory:

1. **conversation-memory.png** - Screenshot or mockup showing conversation memory in action
2. **session-history.png** - Dashboard view with past chat sessions and timestamps
3. **model-selection.png** - Interface showing model selection dropdown with options
4. **streaming-interface.png** - Live streaming response with incremental text appearing

## Image Specifications:
- **Format**: PNG or WebP preferred
- **Dimensions**: 1100x700px (16:10 aspect ratio) or similar
- **Style**: Match the graphite/teal Carbon Teal theme
- **Background**: Dark (#121516) with teal accents (#14b8a6)
- **Content**: Actual screenshots from the chat interface showing each feature

## Creating Placeholder Images:
If you don't have the actual screenshots yet, you can create simple placeholders:
1. Use a dark graphite background (#121516)
2. Add teal accent borders/highlights (#14b8a6)
3. Include descriptive text and mock UI elements
4. Use the same font as the application (Segoe UI, Roboto, etc.)

The images will display at max-width: 550px on desktop with automatic responsive scaling on mobile.
